html
  head
  body(style="margin:0; padding:0; background:linear-gradient(135deg, #003300, #000000, #001f3f);font-family:Arial, sans-serif; color:#fff; text-align:center;")
    div(style="max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; padding:40px;")

      div
        h1(style="color:#00ff99; font-size:32px; margin-bottom:20px; text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #000;"
        ) Vault Money

      div
        h2(style="font-size:24px; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:20px;")
          | Greetings #{name}, validate your email

        p(style="font-size:16px; margin-bottom:30px;")
          | Click the button below to validate your email:

        a(
  href=validationLink, 
  target="_blank", 
  style="display:inline-block; background:linear-gradient(90deg, #00cc66, #00bfff); color:#000; padding:15px 30px; font-size:16px; font-weight:bold; border-radius:5px; text-decoration:none; box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0, 200, 200, 0.4); margin:20px auto; transition:all 0.3s ease;"
) Validate Email


        p(style="font-size:14px; color:#ccc; margin-top:40px;")
          | Validate your email #{email} to continue with your registration.

        p(style="font-size:14px; color:#aaa; margin-top:20px;")
          | If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email.

        hr(style="margin:40px auto; width:60%; border:1px solid #222;")

        small(style="color:#555; font-size:12px;")
          | © 2025 Vault Money. All rights reserved.
